# Shift

![preview](./preview.png)

## Tips

* CC:
  * emcc
* LDFLAGS:
  * -s EXPORT_ES6=1 
  * -s EXPORTED_RUNTIME_METHODS=FS
  * -s ALLOW_MEMORY_GROWTH=1
